<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About This Project</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css"> <!-- Font Awesome for icons -->
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 35px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #5c67a3;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #777;
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        section h2 {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: black;
        }

        section p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        footer p {
            color: #777;
        }

        .back-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #5c67a3;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .back-btn:hover {
            background-color: #445182;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container" >
        <header>
            <h1>Question Tracker</h1>
            <h2>About This Project</h2>
            <p>Your ultimate solution for tracking and managing your coding questions</p>
        </header>
        <section>
            <h2>Project Overview</h2>
            <p>This project is designed to help developers and coding enthusiasts keep track of their coding questions, upload new questions, make notes, and save useful links.</p>
            <p>Whether you are preparing for coding interviews, practicing problems, or simply keeping a record of interesting challenges, this project aims to be your go-to tool.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Upload and track coding questions</li>
                <li>Add detailed notes for each question</li>
                <li>Save and manage useful links</li>
                <li>Search through your questions with ease</li>
                <li>Secure and user-friendly interface</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>How to Use</h2>
            <p>Getting started is easy:</p>
            <ol style="">
                <li>Sign up or log in to your account</li>
                <li>Navigate to the 'Upload a Question' section</li>
                <li>Fill in the details of your question, add notes, and provide a link if available</li>
                <li>Submit the form to add the question to your collection</li>
                <li>Use the search functionality to find and review your questions anytime</li>
            </ol>
        </section>
        <a href="/profile"><button class="back-btn"><i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i> Back to Profile</button></a>
        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Project Tracker. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
